## 7. Dependency management

### 7.1. Update routine

–°–Љ. `maintenance-playbook.md` Part A. –Ъ—А–∞—В–Ї–Є–µ –њ—А–∞–≤–Є–ї–∞:

- **Security patches (CVE) вАФ automerge** –µ—Б–ї–Є CI green (Dependabot / Renovate config)
- **Patch versions (no CVE) вАФ weekly review + merge** if no breakage
- **Minor versions вАФ biweekly review** + manual merge after smoke test
- **Major versions вАФ quarterly evaluation** + dedicated PR —Б migration plan

### 7.2. Local update workflow

```sh
make deps-outdated   # show outdated deps
make deps-update     # interactive update (asks per package)
make deps-audit      # security audit (npm audit / pip-audit / cargo audit / etc)
```

### 7.3. Lockfile discipline

- `package-lock.json` / `pnpm-lock.yaml` / `poetry.lock` / `Cargo.lock` / `go.sum` вАФ **always committed**
- CI verifies lockfile consistency (`pnpm install --frozen-lockfile`)
- Merge conflicts in lockfile вАФ regenerate from scratch (delete + reinstall), –љ–µ manual edit

